    "At ν = -3, broadly speaking, electron-phonon coupling and short-range Coulomb contribution favor antiferromagnetic and ferromagnetic alignments respectively, though this can in principle depend on the competition between various terms in the Hartree-Fock energy functional.",
    "The observation of a charge Kekulé pattern for the IKS near ν = -2 [25,26] indicates that electron-phonon coupling dominates, which leads us to expect the IKS at ν = -3 to have antiferromagnetic alignment, with the additional caveat that the parameter regime for phonons to dominate has some weak dependence on the filling factor.",
